Everyone is passionate about product excellence - but in reality, is it possible to achieve?

This interactive discussion will lay the foundation for 
how to define product excellence in your organization, product team according to your own standards; 
recognize the 7 phases of the product management lifecycle; 
understand perspectives of customers, users and others consuming your code, and isolate soft skills to help you communicate, collaborate and align with non-technical team members

